Regs</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Program\">Program</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hsl</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StraightLine.html#Cslib.URM.Program.IsStraightLine\">IsStraightLine</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Regs\">Regs</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Regs\">Regs</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The final registers after running a straight-line program from given starting registers. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StraightLine.html#Cslib.URM.straightLine_finalRegs","kind":"def","line":113,"name":"Cslib.URM.straightLine_finalRegs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/StraightLine.lean#L113-L115"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StraightLine.html#Cslib.URM.straightLine_finalState_spec\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">straightLine_finalState_spec</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Program\">Program</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hsl</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StraightLine.html#Cslib.URM.Program.IsStraightLine\">IsStraightLine</